<figureCitation id="8489C8A7220121A0BD625C7C57837420" captionStart="Figures 10–16" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 10 - 16. Synaldis cauca sp. n.: 10 head in dorsal view 11 head in lateral view 12 mandible 13 paraclypeal pit 14 propodeum 15 hind femur 16 tergites 1 - 2." httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11530" pageId="2" pageNumber="69">Figures 10-16</figureCitation>
